    "Themes are Svelte components rendered server-side - same component powers live preview (CSR) and hosted page (SSR), no duplication",
    "Rust PDF microservice is a thin HTTP wrapper around SRG - receives HTML string, returns PDF bytes, stateless and horizontally scalable",
    "Subdomain routing via wildcard DNS and host-header parsing, not per-user nginx configs - scales without config reloads",
